lead_paragraph: Jake Gardiner scored a power-play goal at 2:51 of overtime to give the Toronto Maple Leafs a 4-3 victory over the Philadelphia Flyers on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Jake Gardiner Scores in OT, Maple Leafs Beat Flyers 4-3
